\s UVUGANA N’ABANYAMWUKA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Uvugana n’abanyamwuka bari mukirere cy’Umwuka nanjye nshoboza kuhagera kugira ngo mvugane nawe. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nyuzuza imbaraga z’Umwuka shyira mu kirere Cy’Umwuka Mwami kuko abanyamwuka nibo bazaragwa Ubugingo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Igihe kirageze Mwami abasenga Data by’ukuri n’aba musengera mu kuri kandi buzuye Umwuka Wera. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nyuzuza imbaraga z’Umwuka shyira mu kirere Cy’Umwuka Mwami kuko abanyamwuka nibo bazaragwa Ubugingo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Dore iyi si irandwanya Mwami imbuza kwinjira mu Mwuka Mwami nshoboza kuyirenga ndebe kubitagaragara. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nyuzuza imbaraga z’Umwuka shyira mu kirere Cy’Umwuka Mwami kuko abanyamwuka nibo bazaragwa Ubugingo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Umpe amatwi y’Umwuka Mwami kugira ngo mbashe ku kumva umpe amaso y’Umwuka Mwami kugira ngo mbashe kukubona. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nyuzuza imbaraga z’Umwuka shyira mu kirere Cy’Umwuka Mwami kuko abanyamwuka nibo bazaragwa Ubugingo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Nshira mu mbaraga z’Umwuka kugirango ngendane nawe unganirize Mwami nkuko waganiriye n’Aburahamu. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nyuzuza imbaraga z’Umwuka shyira mu kirere Cy’Umwuka Mwami kuko abanyamwuka nibo bazaragwa Ubugingo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Intege nke zindushya Mwami zimbuza kujya mu Mwuka uzukubite zose Mwami maze umpe ibihe byo gusenga.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nyuzuza imbaraga z’Umwuka shyira mu kirere Cy’Umwuka Mwami kuko abanyamwuka nibo bazaragwa Ubugingo.\bdit*
